readable.content: A dog is preparing to run away from a person interacting with it . A person in a red coat and a running black and brown dog . A woman in a black and orange jacket throws a stick for a brown and black dog to fetch . a woman in a red jacket watches as a black and brown dog runs away from her in woodland clearing . Outside by the trees , a woman wearing jeans and red jacket throws something for a German shepherd to chase .
